-- China to Step Up Study on Carbon Market, Help With Financing, PBOC Yi Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-16T02:40:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-16/china-to-step-up-study-on-carbon-market-help-with-financing-pboc-yi-says.html
The Chinese government will step up
its study on the carbon market, finance support of companies’
purchases of energy-saving equipment and spur low-carbon
consumption, said Yi Cheng, deputy director with the research
bureau of the People’s Bank of China.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
